@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hiuzex(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((v0 + 0.64 / v2 + 0.74)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.28 * v0 + 0.60)) * wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.99)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(v1) / 0.25)
    v2 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.94 / v2 + 0.08)) / (wp.cos(v0 + 0.71) + v1))
    data[tid] = v0
